text: This is one of those bus stops that is awkwardly important. If you're taking a bus, the previous or latter bus stops will be better, because of the shelter and the accessibility to the other buses. You honestly have no real reason to change here. That said, if you're heading to Cathay or SMU SOE or YMCA, then this is your bus stop.
